            <h1 id="hero-heading" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond','Times New Roman',serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4.6vw,34px);line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:0.02em;margin:0 0 10px 0;">
              Coaching for principled, fearless living
            </h1>
            <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#8d7564;margin:0 0 14px 0;">
              Drawing from years in Buddhist monasteries, Circling, and deep relational study,
              I offer one-on-one sessions for people ready to meet life.
            </p>
            <div style="font-size:15px;color:#8d7564;margin:0 0 0 8px;">
              <div style="margin:4px 0;"><span style="color:#b0673c;margin-right:10px;">∿</span>beginner mindfulness</div>
              <div style="margin:4px 0;"><span style="color:#b0673c;margin-right:10px;">∿</span>advanced meditation</div>
              <div style="margin:4px 0;"><span style="color:#b0673c;margin-right:10px;">∿</span>emotional &amp; physical wellbeing</div>
              <div style="margin:4px 0;"><span style="color:#b0673c;margin-right:10px;">∿</span>intimacy &amp; relationships</div>
              <div style="margin:4px 0;"><span style="color:#b0673c;margin-right:10px;">∿</span>principled, resilient living</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Hero photo -->
          <div style="flex:0 0 260px;max-width:260px;min-width:200px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
