          Begin the conversation
        </h3>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:#8d7564;margin:0 0 10px 0;">
          A simple, honest message is enough.
        </p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:18px;margin-top:6px;">
          <div style="flex:1 1 260px;min-width:0;">
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 7px 0;">
              The greatest challenge now is simply finding the people who need this.
              If something in you feels called — even quietly — you’re welcome to reach out.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 7px 0;">
              Share a few lines about where you’re at, what you’re longing for, and any questions you have.
              I’ll respond with next steps and a way to schedule.
            </p>
